Episode 4: Rocker Jack White


On "Serious Jibber-Jabber," Conan O'Brien has lengthy, uninterrupted conversations with interesting people on topics which fascinate him.

In this special episode shot entirely on 35mm film, Conan and Grammy-winning musician/producer Jack White talk for over an hour over drinks about art, success, and upholstery. Yes, upholstery.
